    <h1 class="main-title">Cryptographic Techniques Details 📚</h1>

    <div class="technique">
        <h3 class="technique-title">🔄 Caesar Cipher</h3>
        <p>A simple substitution cipher that shifts letters by a fixed number of positions.</p>
        <div class="example">
            Original word: HELLO<br>
            Numerical values: H(7) E(4) L(11) L(11) O(14)<br>
            Key = 3<br>
            After adding key: 10 7 14 14 17<br>
            After mod 26: 10 7 14 14 17<br>
            Encrypted text: KHOOR
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique">
        <h3 class="technique-title">🔑 Vigenère Cipher</h3>
        <p>A polyalphabetic substitution cipher using a keyword to shift letters.</p>
        <div class="example">
            Word: HELLO<br>
            Key: KEY<br>
            Word numbers: H(7) E(4) L(11) L(11) O(14)<br>
            Key numbers: K(10) E(4) Y(24) K(10) E(4)<br>
            Sum: 17 8 35 21 18<br>
            After mod 26: 17 8 9 21 18<br>
            Encrypted text: RIJVS
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique">
        <h3 class="technique-title">🚂 Rail Fence Cipher</h3>
        <p>A transposition cipher that writes text in a zigzag pattern on multiple rails.</p>
        <div class="example">
            Word: HELLO<br>
            Rail depth: 3<br>
            <table>
                <tr><td>H</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>O</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>E</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>L</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
            </table>
            Reading by rows: H + O + E + L = HOLE
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="technique">
        <h3 class="technique-title">🔒 RSA Algorithm</h3>
        <p>An asymmetric cryptographic algorithm based on the factorization of large numbers.</p>
        <div class="example">
            p = 3, q = 11, e = 7, n = 33<br>
            Word: HI<br>
            H(7): C = 7^7 mod 33 = 7<br>
            I(8): C = 8^7 mod 33 = 8<br>
            Encrypted text: 7,8
        </div>
    </div>

